{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding the functionality of ChatGPT in information gathering, it was observed that although it facilitates quick access to information, its effectiveness in adequately managing bibliographic references is lower than that of traditional methods, as evidenced by the better performance of the control group in this aspect.In terms of generating precise and relevant research content, ChatGPT proved to be highly effective, as the experimental group outperformed the control group in precision, coherence, and originality of the content produced, indicating its value in improving the quality of research work.In terms of usability for developing research competencies, the experimental group performed better in coherence, originality, depth of content, and problem-solving ability, demonstrating that ChatGPT helps structure ideas and address complex problems more effectively.",
    "However, to maximize these benefits and overcome the limitations in information gathering, it is essential to integrate the use of ChatGPT with traditional teaching methods and rigorous research practices, ensuring an ethical and effective use of technology for comprehensive development of research competencies in students.The use of ChatGPT can enhance students' research competencies by facilitating information gathering and generating relevant content.",
    "However, its effectiveness depends on students' ability to use the tool critically and complement it with traditional research methods.",
    "The integration of ChatGPT into educational processes should be accompanied by appropriate training to maximize its benefits and minimize its limitations.",
    "The research on the impact of ChatGPT in developing investigative competencies in students revealed several limitations and offered future recommendations."
  ]
}